      "content": "but you don't understand. it's not just a mistake or a system error. the foundation itself is rotten. i look at my work now and i just feel sick. people looked up to me, they trusted my data... and it was all built on nothing. i feel like i'm just playing a part in a joke that everyone's eventually going to realize. there's no coming back from this. i've lost my entire identity.",
